animeTitle: Daiyoshi P Produce Ashita no Jobuubu
animeDescription: A collaboration between Taka no Tsume and the Town Work, an employment office whose mascot is a pig called Jobuubu (a play on words of "job" and the Japanese onomatopoeia sounds a pig makes).
animeRelated: ['Parent story: Himitsukessha Taka no Tsume MAX', 'Other: Taka no Tsume GO: Utsukushiki Elleair Shoushuu Plus', 'Alternative version: Taka no Tsume 7: Joou Heika no Jobuubu']
